; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/520
; Description: currency_accounts plugin should generate Open directives for
;              the currency tracking accounts it creates (e.g., Equity:Currency:USD)
; Expected: No errors - plugin generates Open directives like Python beancount

option "operating_currency" "EUR"

plugin "beancount.plugins.currency_accounts" "Equity:Currency"

2026-01-01 open Assets:Bank:EUR
2026-01-01 open Assets:Bank:USD

; Multi-currency transaction with price annotation
; currency_accounts should create:
;   - 2026-01-01 open Equity:Currency:USD
;   - Add neutralizing posting to Equity:Currency:USD
2026-03-17 * "Currency exchange"
  Assets:Bank:EUR       -100 EUR @ 1.10 USD
  Assets:Bank:USD        110 USD
